permit.t.sol
├── when `deadline` is smaller than `block.timestamp`
│   └──  it should revert
└── when `deadline` is bigger or equal than `block.timestamp`
	├── when recovered signer is different from owner
	│   └──  it should revert
	└── when recovered signer is equal to owner
		├── when asset ID is bigger or equal to asset count
		│	└──  it should revert
		└──	when asset ID is smaller than asset count
			├── it should update `isApprovedForAsset` to true
			├── it should increment nonce
			└──	it should emit `ApprovalForAsset`
